#: ../../M/misbug.rst:9
msgid ""
"[MIT; rare (like its referent)] An unintended property of a program that "
"turns out to be useful; something that should have been a :ref:`bug` but "
"turns out to be a :ref:`feature`\\. Compare :ref:`green-lightning`\\. See "
":ref:`miswart`\\."
msgstr ""
"[MIT。(その指示対象同様)稀]役に立つと判明したプログラムの意図しない性質。\\ :ref:`bug`\\ であるべきだったのに\\ "
":ref:`feature`\\ と判明したもの。\\ :ref:`green-lightning`\\ と比較せよ。\\ "
":ref:`miswart`\\ を参照。"
